Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  今天你也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大门要关好啊  太不小心了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  洗发水用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不～
